Step 1: upgrade anaconda (or make sure it is up to date)
python -m pip install --upgrade pip

Step 2: update latest panda
conda install -c anaconda pandas


Step 3: update scipy (optional)


Step 4: install nlp packages spacy
conda install -c conda-forge spacy

Step5: install gensim
conda install -c anaconda gensim

Step6: install textblob
conda install -c conda-forge textblob

step7: install wordcloud
conda install -c conda-forge wordcloud

Step8: install pyLDAvis
conda install -c conda-forge pyldavis

Step9: install plotly
conda install -c plotly plotly

Step10: install streamlit
conda install -c conda-forge streamlit

Step11: install openpyxl
conda install -c anaconda openpyxl

issues with protobuf
pip install --upgrade protobuf
